headline: Tenet Beats Q1 Earnings on Strong Ambulatory Unit, Ups '25 EPS View
summary: THC's first-quarter results benefit on the back of higher net revenue per case and the expansion of service lines within the Ambulatory Care unit. It currently expects 2025 adjusted EPS within $11.99-$13.12.
